@Lifegainwithbite  

[Torpor Orb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Torpor Orb) would indeed counter the ability. Alternatively, [Platinum Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Platinum Angel) at the same CMC would work, and can be cheated out. [Stifle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stifle) is another option, but takes an extra blue mana on top of the cost for Phage herself.  

You could always get lucky with 4 [Dark Ritual](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Ritual)s on turn 1, if you know it's safe from removal.
